*Obe* su bile zadovoljne izborom (Both were satisfied with the choice).

*Oba* su deteta znala za istinu (Both children knew the truth).

*Oboje* su se trudili da završe zadatak (Both of them tried to finish the task).

*Obe* su činile napore da se pomire (Both of them made efforts to reconcile).

*Obojici* se to nije svidjalo (Both of them did not like it).